longBusinessSummary: Banco Pan S.A., together with its subsidiaries, operates as a middle-sized financial institution in Brazil. It provides payroll loans, vehicle financing, and credit cards. The company also offers services in the areas of consortium, insurance, securitization of real estate, and agribusiness receivables. In addition, it provides investment products, such as bank deposit certificates, real estate and agribusiness letters of credit, financial bills, interbank deposits, and Eurobonds. The company distributes its products and services through correspondent banks, authorized dealerships, multi-brand new and used vehicle shops, and real estate partners. It operates through 60 service branches. The company was formerly known as Banco Panamericano S.A. and changed its name to Banco Pan S.A. in August 2014.
